quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  82,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  82,1,jab aasman phatt jaye ga
  82,2,aur jab tarre jhar parrin ge
  82,3,aur jab darya beh ( kar aik dosray se mil ) jayen ge
  82,4,aur jab qabrain akheer di jayen gi
  82,5,tab har shakhs maloom karle ga ke is ne agaykiya bheja tha aur peechaykiya chorra tha
  82,6,ae ensaan tujh ko apne perwar-digaar karam gastar ke baab mein kis cheez ne dhoka diya
  82,7,( wohi to hai ) jis ne tujhe banaya aur ( tairay aaza ko ) theekkiya aur ( tairay qaamat ko ) motadil rakha
  82,8,aur jis soorat mein chaha tujhe joor diya
  82,9,magar behat tum log jaza ko jutlatay ho
  82,10,halaank tum par nigehbaan muqarrar hain
  82,11,aliiiii qader ( tumhari baton ke ) likhnay walay
  82,12,jo tum karte ho woh usay jantay hain
  82,13,be shak nekokaar nematon ( ki bahisht ) mein hon ge .
  82,14,aur badkirdar dozakh mein
  82,15,( yani ) jaza ke din is mein daakhil hon ge
  82,16,aur is se choup nahi saken ge
  82,17,aur tumhekiya maloom ke jaza ka din kaisa hai ?
  82,18,phir tumhekiya maloom ke jaza ka din kaisa hai ?
  82,19,jis roz koi kisi ka bhala nah kar sakay ga aur hukum is roz khuda hi ka ho ga
